English

Facilitation model 4/7
Involvement
Engagement
Involvement and Engagement
2 key elements that boost audience participation are Involvement & Engagement
When you as a facilitator involve your participants - instead of endless solo speech - they will get more engaged in the meeting with higher quality results.
And engagement boosts involvement ...and the positive spiral is running.
